2. Why this technique works

Human cognition is pattern-driven.

When a symbol appears repeatedly across domains, the mind builds a concept lattice.

Example:

seed → biology
seed → agriculture
seed → genetics
seed → ideas

Soon the symbol means all of those at once.

This creates a high-density concept node.

